description: Demolition of existing building; erection of 3 buildings ranging from 3 to 7 storeys with basement, comprising self-contained residential units with commercial space at ground floor level to Block A; creation of new street, associated landscaping, car and cycle parking, private and communal amenity space subject to a Deed of Agreement under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
